 Put in for a pass yesterday , expect I wont get it for I believ all leav is knock on the head till the 4th of Oct. on account of the railway strike . Charli Tonkin one of my old platoon Cpls came across from the OTB. to see me tonight he got hit a few day after me has just come from Hurdcott . I was pleas to see him for he is a veri decent chap , we went for a stroll togeth had a yarn over old time . Has been rain on off the whole afternoon it look veri showeri tonight The Railway strike end today but unfortun all leav has been cancel till the 4th to get the line in run order again , this has been a veri unpopular strike among the peopl for they went out on strike against even their own
